data.description: Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this meticulously renovated home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 baths, and an adaptable 4th room that can be utilized as a bedroom or office, conveniently positioned at the entrance of the house. Sprawled across nearly 1800 sqft, the open-concept living and dining area invites warmth and abundant natural light, accentuating the beautifully remodeled kitchen - a chef’s delight equipped with modern appliances. Every corner of this home speaks of modern sophistication and comfort. Recently updated with a new carpet and gutters installed in November 2022, and partially new windows fitted by the previous owner in 2022, this residence combines contemporary aesthetics with functional living. The appliances, including a double-door refrigerator, washer/dryer, dishwasher, stove, and microwave, along with the window blinders, are included to ensure a seamless transition into your new home. Outside, a lush, expansive backyard adorned with beautiful trees and a storage shed, awaits for those moments of relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. A hook for water filter/softener is thoughtfully placed in the garage. A new roof was installed in 2021 and has a transferrable warranty, a lifetime warranty for foundation repaired in 2022, an AC warranty, and a 5-year gutter warranty. Located within walking distance to all three RRISD schools and ensconced in a low-tax-rate area. The low monthly HOA fee grants access to a community park and pool, fostering a vibrant and welcoming neighborhood ambience.
